title: Nordo in for PA! Carline/Gleeman/Bercich/Birk/Krawczynski
description: Nordo is in for PA today! Peter Carline calls in from across the pond to talk about England's World Cup run and the latest NFL news, Aaron Gleeman talks Twins baseball, Pete Bercich talks about his Croatian roots and Vikings training camp, Matt Birk makes his regular appearance and Jonny Athletic calls in from Vegas to talk Timberwolves basketball!
